test_large_range:
assert [6, 7, 8, 9] == [7, 8, 9]
  At index 0 diff: 6 != 7
  Left contains one more item: 9
  Full diff:
  - [7, 8, 9]
  + [6, 7, 8, 9]
  ?  +++
test_even_range:
assert [12, 14, 16, 18] == [14, 16, 18]
  At index 0 diff: 12 != 14
  Left contains one more item: 18
  Full diff:
  - [14, 16, 18]
  + [12, 14, 16, 18]
  ?  ++++
